[TranslatorEvent1]
Message="2) On Tauri, locals longed for wealth and power, so they created the Skaarj, who then conquered the Krall world. The Skaarj then turned against them, and began looting other worlds. Later, they created the Mercs on Sirius, tasking them to destroy the Skaarj."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent2]
Message="My Log: These are the only doors, that open. Maybe I can find a way to get into the others."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent3]
Message="We got a call from planet Sirius. It is already occupied by the Skaarj. Our last few Mercenaries are hidden in this dungeon. Sadly, we had to leave our technology. The Skaarj can detect us because of it."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent4]
Message="Looks like we'll have to stay hidden in these cellars. Our spies have found Brutes, who want to start a war against the Skaarj. They think that they can defeat the Krall."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent5]
Message="My Log: It's true, the Mercenaries really are hiding from the Skaarj. Perhaps their leader is here too."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent6]
Message="My Log: So I finally got past the last door. Let's see what we have next."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent7]
Message="My Log: So that's it. The Mercenary leader is dead. So the next enemy race is now on its way to extinction. Next, the Brutes. I know the location of their planet: Pharao."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent8]
Message="Recently, Brutes started leaving planet Pharao. In a couple of days they destroyed the Krall and plan to expand into other planets, starting a war against the Skaarj. They think the Skaarj betrayed them."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent9]
Message="My Log: Maybe it would be good to check here. Perhaps there will be someone in the library."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent10]
Message="My Log: Here's something interesting: The location of planet Pharao and the position of the gate here at Chicken Itza. That's what I need!"
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent11]
Message="1) For many years, races enslaved and devastated the planet. Once, on planet Haros, there was a scientist from the planet Tauri. After years of research, he created the Krall race. Later, he began to expand his research further into space."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent12]
Message="3) The Brutes lived for a long time on planet Pharao. Their origin is not exactly known, maybe a scientist created them. Fortunately they haven't left the planet. All signs show that they will plunder and enslave."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"
